From that She called Him, and Christ word comes from Krishna.

257
00:17:59,160 --> 00:18:03,330
So She call Him Christ

258
00:18:03,620 --> 00:18:06,990
and Yesu or Jesus.

259
00:18:07,160 --> 00:18:11,540
We too call Yeshoda sometimes Jesu or Yesu.

260
00:18:11,750 --> 00:18:14,080
So She called Him by that name

261
00:18:14,330 --> 00:18:20,160
and that is how She put the link for us to understand

262
00:18:20,370 --> 00:18:24,700
how close He was to Shri Krishna.

263
00:18:26,950 --> 00:18:31,200
Shri Krisha came only, incarnated only in India

264
00:18:31,410 --> 00:18:34,620
because He would have been

265
00:18:34,830 --> 00:18:38,290
too lenient person to be incarnated in America.

266
00:18:38,500 --> 00:18:44,040
As it is they have no limitations, they have no maryadas,

267
00:18:44,250 --> 00:18:48,540
they have no idea of dharma, they are very great adharmis.

268
00:18:48,750 --> 00:18:52,450
So only a person like Christ

269
00:18:52,660 --> 00:18:58,330
who is absolutely pure, wise,

270
00:18:58,540 --> 00:19:01,990
and does not believe

271
00:19:02,160 --> 00:19:06,540
in the leela part of Shri Krishna.

272
00:19:06,790 --> 00:19:10,040
Is Shri Krishna said that is this all leela

273
00:19:10,250 --> 00:19:15,580
to overcome the strictness of Shri Rama.

274
00:19:15,790 --> 00:19:18,790
But Christ did not said so

275
00:19:18,990 --> 00:19:24,500
and despite that, all over wherever Christianity is practiced,

276
00:19:24,700 --> 00:19:27,500
they think it's all leela, adharma is leela,

277
00:19:27,700 --> 00:19:30,910
whatever wrong we do is leela, after all, all innocent.

278
00:19:31,120 --> 00:19:33,790
It's surprising. Their logic is so funny

279
00:19:33,990 --> 00:19:36,620
I've never been able to understand their logic.

280
00:19:36,830 --> 00:19:40,410
All self-destructive, nonsensical logic they have.

281
00:19:40,620 --> 00:19:44,450
So, for us Indians, we should know that we have

282
00:19:44,660 --> 00:19:48,450
full idea of dharma. We know what is wrong and what is good.

283
00:19:48,660 --> 00:19:52,330
But more credit I would give to Christians,

284
00:19:52,540 --> 00:19:58,870
who are from such countries where they have no idea of Kundalini,

285
00:19:59,040 --> 00:20:01,580
have come up so much

286
00:20:01,790 --> 00:20:05,950
and have become such great Sahaja Yogis.

287
00:20:06,120 --> 00:20:08,250
Now is the blessing of God,

288
00:20:08,450 --> 00:20:12,250
because they were genuine, they were sincere.

289
00:20:12,500 --> 00:20:17,870
It is Christ who brought them to Sahaja Yoga.

290
00:20:18,040 --> 00:20:20,830
Without Him it would not have been possible.

291
00:20:21,000 --> 00:20:24,990
Here Shri Ganesha is just a symbol, sort of a thing.

292
00:20:25,160 --> 00:20:28,540
He resides in the stones.

293
00:20:28,750 --> 00:20:34,250
But there He incarnated and He told people what is dharma is,

294
00:20:34,450 --> 00:20:38,830
which they are supposed to follow, but they never follow.

295
00:20:39,040 --> 00:20:44,200
They never follow. They are extremely money oriented people.

296
00:20:44,500 --> 00:20:50,500
Is very surprising what things they have done in the name of God.

297
00:20:52,040 --> 00:20:55,040
The most symbolic thing is His birth.

298
00:20:55,250 --> 00:20:59,250
He was born in a manger,

299
00:20:59,450 --> 00:21:02,120
just imagine, in a manger,

300
00:21:02,330 --> 00:21:06,830
full of straws assembled together

301
00:21:07,000 --> 00:21:09,160
this child was born,

302
00:21:09,370 --> 00:21:13,870
where there were other animals used to be.

303
00:21:14,040 --> 00:21:17,990
See the way

304
00:21:18,200 --> 00:21:20,950
this great incarnation took birth.

305
00:21:21,160 --> 00:21:27,040
He was not king, he was not a big rich man,

306
00:21:27,250 --> 00:21:31,750
He was born as a very poor person

307
00:21:31,990 --> 00:21:37,910
and in a place which is something very much

308
00:21:38,080 --> 00:21:41,750
below the human standard.

309
00:21:41,950 --> 00:21:45,990
This message is, that you don't need palaces,

310
00:21:46,160 --> 00:21:48,870
you don't need huge places to be born,

311
00:21:49,040 --> 00:21:53,290
you can be born anywhere, if you are a pure Spirit,

312
00:21:53,500 --> 00:21:54,910
if you are Christ.

313
00:21:55,080 --> 00:21:58,870
Such a great personality was born like that.

314
00:21:59,080 --> 00:22:01,790
Now the other way round people go.

315
00:22:01,990 --> 00:22:06,160
They are extremely money oriented, very materialistic.

316
00:22:06,370 --> 00:22:08,330
I mean to such a limit

317
00:22:08,540 --> 00:22:12,120
that you can't understand what  are they up to.

318
00:22:12,330 --> 00:22:15,790
They are destroying themselves with whatever money they have made,

319
00:22:15,990 --> 00:22:18,290
they have no sense, they have no proportion.

320
00:22:18,500 --> 00:22:20,990
This is what is happening in the West,

321
00:22:21,160 --> 00:22:24,000
and we are trying to follow them also.

322
00:22:24,250 --> 00:22:27,250
We are trying to follow their destructive methods

323
00:22:27,500 --> 00:22:31,540
and we are trying to think that we are very advanced.

324
00:22:31,750 --> 00:22:35,160
Advanced towards doom, that's what they are.

325
00:22:35,370 --> 00:22:38,330
We have to be very careful with our children,

326
00:22:38,540 --> 00:22:41,990
with our relations, that we don't go to their dirty things

327
00:22:42,160 --> 00:22:45,410
and take to their dirty ways,

328
00:22:45,620 --> 00:22:51,200
which they have created in the name of God, in the name of God.

329
00:22:52,500 --> 00:22:58,500
Now this group that we have here, is quite a large group,

330
00:22:59,160 --> 00:23:01,700
and we are Sahaja Yogis

331
00:23:01,910 --> 00:23:03,750
we are all blessed people,

332
00:23:03,950 --> 00:23:06,450
we know what is Divinity is

333
00:23:06,660 --> 00:23:09,250
and we know what Christ is.

334
00:23:09,500 --> 00:23:15,370
Whether you are born Hindu or anything, makes no difference,

335
00:23:15,580 --> 00:23:17,620
because Christ is universal.

336
00:23:17,830 --> 00:23:19,250
He's the support of universe,

337
00:23:19,450 --> 00:23:22,080
that's what is written in Devi Mahatmyam

338
00:23:22,290 --> 00:23:25,870
ki ("that" in Hindi) He will be the support of the universe.

339
00:23:26,040 --> 00:23:28,660
So one has to understand

340
00:23:28,870 --> 00:23:33,620
that we should never ridicule anybody, if he is following Christ

341
00:23:33,830 --> 00:23:38,500
and that we should worship Him with the same affection,

342
00:23:38,700 --> 00:23:42,750
with the same devotion, with the same surrendering,

343
00:23:42,950 --> 00:23:46,200
as we worship Shri Ganesh.

344
00:23:46,410 --> 00:23:48,790
Because I don't think Christians

345
00:23:48,990 --> 00:23:53,370
have any faith about Christ, no faith.

346
00:23:53,580 --> 00:23:56,370
They are, "We believe in Christ, we believe in Christ.

347
00:23:56,580 --> 00:24:00,660
You cure my father, do this, do that".

348
00:24:00,990 --> 00:24:05,160
But as Sahaja Yogis' faith works.

349
00:24:05,410 --> 00:24:08,790
Your faith is an enlightened faith and it works.

350
00:24:08,990 --> 00:24:12,620
But you must have faith in yourself, in Sahaja Yoga,

351
00:24:12,830 --> 00:24:15,120
and in the life you are leading.

352
00:24:15,330 --> 00:24:17,250
Unless and until this happens to you

353
00:24:17,450 --> 00:24:20,040
you shouldn't call yourself a Sahaja Yogi.

354
00:24:20,250 --> 00:24:23,750
I see, still there are people on the periphery.

355
00:24:23,950 --> 00:24:26,200
Then you don't know what to do about it,

356
00:24:26,410 --> 00:24:29,950
you don't understand in a mental way,

357
00:24:30,120 --> 00:24:35,040
but you just float into the immense love of God

358
00:24:35,250 --> 00:24:38,790
and you want to give this love to others.

359
00:24:38,990 --> 00:24:43,580
But still, materialism becomes subtler with some people.

360
00:24:43,790 --> 00:24:45,790
They are still materialistic.

361
00:24:45,990 --> 00:24:47,750
They are materialistic in the sense,

362
00:24:47,950 --> 00:24:52,990
they still think of earning in a bad way some money or something.

363
00:24:53,200 --> 00:24:55,450
Maybe, but that is not so common.

364
00:24:55,660 --> 00:24:57,580
But I feel they are now

365
00:24:57,790 --> 00:25:01,000
suddenly started getting attached to their children.

366
00:25:01,250 --> 00:25:04,830
This attachment is very wrong.

367
00:25:05,000 --> 00:25:09,950
You see, children belong to Sahaja Yoga. You have no right on them.

368
00:25:10,250 --> 00:25:15,540
Because they straight away wanted children to come back home

369
00:25:15,750 --> 00:25:18,790
and not to come to Ganapatipule.

370
00:25:18,990 --> 00:25:23,580
Means they are children of Sahaja Yoga.

371
00:25:23,790 --> 00:25:27,160
They have to come to Ganapatipule, no question.

372
00:25:27,370 --> 00:25:30,620
But they wanted to take over their children directly.

373
00:25:30,830 --> 00:25:33,540
Everything is there, directly done.

374
00:25:33,750 --> 00:25:35,990
Is not, children are not here for that.

375
00:25:36,160 --> 00:25:39,160
They are here to grow in Sahaja Yoga. If you don't want

376
00:25:39,370 --> 00:25:41,910
your children to grow in Sahaja Yoga, better take them away.

377
00:25:42,120 --> 00:25:44,790
But this is not the way to behave arbitrarily,

378
00:25:44,990 --> 00:25:47,080
to take the children away from the school,

379
00:25:47,290 --> 00:25:49,200
when everybody is coming to Ganapatipule.

380
00:25:49,410 --> 00:25:51,620
And I'm sure children don't like it.

381
00:25:51,830 --> 00:25:54,040
They would love to be here.

382
00:25:54,250 --> 00:25:57,000
So the materialism in the sense of children,

383
00:25:57,200 --> 00:26:02,660
also saving money part is working out.

384
00:26:03,250 --> 00:26:05,950
And this is, something shows the materialism,

385
00:26:06,120 --> 00:26:11,370
which Christ never, never clung to.

386
00:26:11,620 --> 00:26:14,750
He never wanted it.

387
00:26:17,160 --> 00:26:19,660
This one we have to understand.

388
00:26:19,870 --> 00:26:23,080
To pay respect to Christ the best thing

389
00:26:23,290 --> 00:26:25,950
is to get out of this materialistic ideas.

390
00:26:26,120 --> 00:26:29,000
All right, you have materialistic ideas

391
00:26:29,200 --> 00:26:33,040
as far as I don't say that you don't go to Himalayas,

392
00:26:33,250 --> 00:26:37,990
I don't say that you go to, you,

393
00:26:38,200 --> 00:26:39,830
you practice asceticism,

394
00:26:40,000 --> 00:26:43,120
I don't say take away, give up your children, like Buddha did.

395
00:26:43,330 --> 00:26:44,910
Nothing of the kind.

396
00:26:45,080 --> 00:26:49,620
But your detachment should work.

397
00:26:50,750 --> 00:26:56,040
There's a, say a bird is there, flying over the ocean of water.

398
00:26:56,250 --> 00:27:01,120
It will never drink the water of the ocean, because it is saltish.

399
00:27:01,330 --> 00:27:04,500
You are there, you are in this world,

400
00:27:04,750 --> 00:27:07,580
but you must develop your detachment.

401
00:27:07,790 --> 00:27:09,990
In the beginning it was all right, "my father is sick",

402
00:27:10,160 --> 00:27:11,990
"my mother is sick", "my child is like this",

403
00:27:12,160 --> 00:27:15,330
all this nonsense was all right. But not now.

404
00:27:15,540 --> 00:27:18,500
Now the speed of Sahaja Yoga is very fast

405
00:27:18,700 --> 00:27:22,950
and those will be left behind, will be left behind. So be careful.

406
00:27:23,120 --> 00:27:28,620
Do not get entangled into these materialistic ideas.

407
00:27:30,200 --> 00:27:34,620
And for Indians especially, they don't like to stay in ashrams.

408
00:27:34,830 --> 00:27:38,200
Indians want to have their homes, so they can dominate their wives,

409
00:27:38,410 --> 00:27:42,990
have their special type of food, this, that, and

410
00:27:43,160 --> 00:27:49,120
work out all their ugly tastes all the time.

411
00:27:49,790 --> 00:27:52,250
I would say that's must be the reason people must have said

412
00:27:52,450 --> 00:27:58,450
that Indians must fast, to get rid of their tongues, desires.

413
00:28:00,660 --> 00:28:05,290
They will, even when fast, think about food, what's the use?

414
00:28:05,500 --> 00:28:07,620
Christ fasted for forty days

415
00:28:07,830 --> 00:28:11,370
and Satan asked Him that, "You should give up Your fast

416
00:28:11,580 --> 00:28:16,040
and do this and do that". He never listened.

417
00:28:17,910 --> 00:28:22,580
So materialism works out in two types.

418
00:28:22,910 --> 00:28:27,200
First of all in the West now is the materialism is "my house",

419
00:28:27,410 --> 00:28:32,080
"my wife", "my children", this that.

420
00:28:32,700 --> 00:28:36,540
And in the East is, "what sort of a food I eat",

421
00:28:36,750 --> 00:28:39,620
"what sort of a house I should have",

422
00:28:39,830 --> 00:28:45,080
"what sort of a family I should have?"

423
00:28:46,410 --> 00:28:49,500
All these things are still lingering.

424
00:28:49,700 --> 00:28:53,410
As your ascent has become subtler

425
00:28:53,620 --> 00:28:56,580
they are also becoming subtler and subtler.

426
00:28:56,790 --> 00:28:58,790
And they are holding you back.

427
00:28:58,990 --> 00:29:02,790
There are all kinds of things. For example I know of Sahaja Yogis,

428
00:29:02,990 --> 00:29:07,870
who want to make business out of Sahaja Yoga, there are.

429
00:29:08,040 --> 00:29:09,870
Like these people here, outside,

430
00:29:10,040 --> 00:29:12,830
they want to sell their things to us

431
00:29:13,000 --> 00:29:16,040
and to make money out of this.

432
00:29:16,290 --> 00:29:18,450
There was a demand that there were no saris.

433
00:29:18,660 --> 00:29:22,540
I said, "All right, take saris. But you are not to buy from outside".

434
00:29:22,750 --> 00:29:24,700
Also they will go to some shop here,

435
00:29:24,910 --> 00:29:27,910
and have something to drink, or something to eat,

436
00:29:28,080 --> 00:29:31,120
and then suffer from something.

437
00:29:31,330 --> 00:29:36,120
What is the need? Can you not control your thirst?

438
00:29:36,330 --> 00:29:41,120
Can you not control your appetite?

439
00:29:41,500 --> 00:29:46,160
It's very easy. Did He not do it? Christ did it.

440
00:29:46,450 --> 00:29:48,410
You have come here to worship Him.

441
00:29:48,620 --> 00:29:51,580
Try to control these things are very important,

442
00:29:51,790 --> 00:29:54,580
and once it happens,

443
00:29:54,830 --> 00:29:57,830
it doesn't matter if you get food, doesn't matter,

444
00:29:57,990 --> 00:30:01,120
if you don't get some good place to live in.

445
00:30:01,330 --> 00:30:04,830
You can live anywhere, anywhere.

446
00:30:05,000 --> 00:30:09,410
As far as I am concerned, you know that very well.

447
00:30:09,620 --> 00:30:13,540
I have no demands. I have, I mean My body doesn't demand anything.

448
00:30:13,750 --> 00:30:17,910
Is such a good body. Never demands.

449
00:30:18,080 --> 00:30:23,700
And that's why I have seen, that I never feel tired.

450
00:30:23,910 --> 00:30:29,370
I am here with you and in the same way I am anywhere.

451
00:30:29,620 --> 00:30:32,450
If you make Me sleep here I can sleep the whole night.

452
00:30:32,660 --> 00:30:35,990
My body never says anything.

453
00:30:36,200 --> 00:30:39,910
On the contrary I've seen the experience is very different.

454
00:30:40,080 --> 00:30:42,160
Once I travelled by train,

455
00:30:42,370 --> 00:30:45,700
I think from Pune to Hyderabad or something,

456
00:30:45,910 --> 00:30:47,990
and the train - I was on the wheel -

457
00:30:48,160 --> 00:30:51,250
and the thing was jumping, jumping, jumping all the time.

458
00:30:51,450 --> 00:30:53,990
I slept off and what I was feeling,

459
00:30:54,200 --> 00:30:57,580
that I am going from one star to another star,

460
00:30:57,790 --> 00:30:59,370
moving from the whole universe.

461
00:30:59,580 --> 00:31:02,500
I never felt the jump, I felt the other way round,

462
00:31:02,750 --> 00:31:05,200
that the whole thing is going, the body is moving

463
00:31:05,410 --> 00:31:07,660
from this star to that star, from there to there.

464
00:31:07,870 --> 00:31:13,160
I mean somebody would be absolutely angry for a thing like that.

465
00:31:13,370 --> 00:31:16,200
On the contrary, I was enjoying, nice jumping from here to there

466
00:31:16,410 --> 00:31:18,500
to go into this star and to that star and

467
00:31:18,700 --> 00:31:22,910
moving from one place to another. It was very interesting.

468
00:31:23,080 --> 00:31:25,580
So the reaction is very different.

469
00:31:25,790 --> 00:31:28,950
Reaction is different. If there is a crisis,

470
00:31:29,120 --> 00:31:32,620
suddenly I become thoughtless, completely thoughtless.

471
00:31:32,830 --> 00:31:38,620
And a kind of a tremendous peace starts pouring out of it.

472
00:31:39,040 --> 00:31:41,620
If there is a crisis.

473
00:31:41,830 --> 00:31:45,040
And this is what you all can achieve very simply,

474
00:31:45,250 --> 00:31:48,830
if you get detached.

475
00:31:49,120 --> 00:31:50,910
See, I have children, I have grandchildren.

476
00:31:51,080 --> 00:31:52,620
I never telephone to them.

477
00:31:52,830 --> 00:31:55,990
I'm not bothered. If they telephone, well and good.

478
00:31:56,160 --> 00:31:58,580
I never telephone to my husband also.

479
00:31:58,790 --> 00:32:03,040
I always think that it's a waste of time.

480
00:32:03,250 --> 00:32:05,200
of telephoning here and telephoning...

481
00:32:05,410 --> 00:32:07,330
I've got all telephones within Myself.

482
00:32:07,540 --> 00:32:11,250
I know everybody is all right so why to telephone to them.

483
00:32:11,450 --> 00:32:15,580
But unless and until you develop that kind of status it won't [work].

484
00:32:15,790 --> 00:32:18,700
Then another thing I've noticed about Sahaja Yogis

485
00:32:18,910 --> 00:32:20,700
that they become suddenly very violent

486
00:32:20,910 --> 00:32:24,290
and there are reports that some people were hit.

487
00:32:24,500 --> 00:32:27,700
That's not being a Sahaja Yogi at all.

488
00:32:27,910 --> 00:32:31,870
I've never raise My hand against even My own children.

489
00:32:32,040 --> 00:32:35,660
It's not allowed. Nobody has to raise the hand

490
00:32:35,910 --> 00:32:38,330
or touch somebody's body to be violent.

491
00:32:38,540 --> 00:32:42,500
It's absolutely, such a person will fall very deep down,

492
00:32:42,700 --> 00:32:45,830
into Sahaja Yoga, without doing anything.

493
00:32:46,000 --> 00:32:48,990
You are not to get angry, you are not to shout.

494
00:32:49,160 --> 00:32:52,540
Nothing of the kind is going to help you.

495
00:32:52,750 --> 00:32:56,290
You have to be absolutely peaceful, calm, compassionate.

496
00:32:56,500 --> 00:33:00,990
If there is a wrong type of a man, just tell Me, I'll manage.

497
00:33:01,160 --> 00:33:05,040
You don't have to handle such situations and misbehave,

498
00:33:05,250 --> 00:33:09,790
because you are still attached,

499
00:33:09,990 --> 00:33:12,580
and that attachment will pull you down.

500
00:33:12,870 --> 00:33:15,790
So be careful, not to be angry.

501
00:33:15,990 --> 00:33:17,910
Look at Christ!

502
00:33:18,080 --> 00:33:20,750
He was angry with the people who were selling things

503
00:33:20,950 --> 00:33:24,080
near the church - you know, that time it was not the church,

504
00:33:24,330 --> 00:33:26,160
but they called it a tabernacle.

505
00:33:26,370 --> 00:33:30,160
And He was very angry, that in the temple of God,

506
00:33:30,370 --> 00:33:32,750
these people are selling things outside,

507
00:33:32,950 --> 00:33:36,580
and He took a big hunter and hit them hard. But He was Christ.

508
00:33:36,790 --> 00:33:39,910
But at the same time, when He was crucified,

509
00:33:40,080 --> 00:33:43,580
He said, "Oh God, My Father, please forgive them,

510
00:33:43,790 --> 00:33:47,790
because they don't know what they are doing".

511
00:33:48,410 --> 00:33:52,330
This is what is, one has to understand from Him.

512
00:33:52,540 --> 00:33:56,160
His character, how forgiving, how loving He was.

513
00:33:56,370 --> 00:33:58,540
How He looked after the people,

514
00:33:58,750 --> 00:34:02,330
how He helped people for their emancipation.

515
00:34:02,540 --> 00:34:06,000
In those days of complete chaos

516
00:34:06,200 --> 00:34:09,540
and anarchy,

517
00:34:09,750 --> 00:34:15,700
He stood up and talked about truth and about

518
00:34:15,990 --> 00:34:21,660
