558
00:36:28,580 --> 00:36:32,500
I tell you, if you are a Sahaja Yogi and if you misbehave,

559
00:36:32,700 --> 00:36:34,870
He allows you to some extent.

560
00:36:35,040 --> 00:36:37,370
