00:40:46,290 --> 00:40:48,990
But you being Sahaja Yogis should know about Him,

628
00:40:49,160 --> 00:40:52,620
and must have full respect, full faith in Him.

629
00:40:52,830 --> 00:40:54,750
And He is your eldest brother.

630
00:40:54,950 --> 00:40:59,120
As Shri Ganesha is, He incarnates as your elder brother.

